Class GenericOperation

  • java.lang.Object
    • expressionParser.ExprNode
      • expressionParser.OperandNode
        • operations.GenericOperation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IVisitable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EqOperation, GeOperation, GtOperation, LeOperation, LtOperation, NeOperation

    public abstract class GenericOperation
extends OperandNode
    GenericOperation class is an abstract class that contains the reference value or the reference name of the OperationNode, depending on the type of node (eq, ne node for name or le, lt, ge, gt, eq, ne node for value).
    Author:
    razvan
